message.content:
My white or my black?" Nigel enquired.
"Now I wonder which I wore at that
particular surgery?" "You are a fool,
darling," Di said happily. "I shall take
great pleasure in telling that young man
exactly what you were doing that
evening." "No, don't," he said, after
kissing her again. "I rather like to have
the housemen think of me as a
two-timing Don Juan.
